    <h3 class="strong-type f2 f1-ns tc colour-p ttu">My Story</h3>
    <img src="/images/mel_and_girls.jpg" alt="Mel and her girls" class="mw-100 db center mt3 mb5">
    <p class="measure-wide lh-copy colour-p tc center body-type f4 ph3">A mum to two amazing girls, and an Advanced Birth & Beyond practitioner (UoW) with a background in Nursing and Complimentary Therapies, I been working with families as a doula and childbirth educator since 2005.  My commitment to promoting, and improving, positive birth and parenting experiences has resulted in continual learning and research into birth trauma, perinatal mental health and the integral role this plays in early childhood development.</p>
